                                                                     https://brentwood-home-products.imgix.net/{{ imgName }}?w=480&fit=crop&dpr=2&fp-x=0.5&fp-y=0.5&fp-z=1&fp-debug=false 2x,
                                                                     https://brentwood-home-products.imgix.net/{{ imgName }}?w=480&fit=crop&dpr=3&fp-x=0.5&fp-y=0.5&fp-z=1&fp-debug=false 3x" 
